org.streaminer.stream.classifier.tree

Class RegressionTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.streaminer.stream.learner.AbstractRegressor<Data>
      • org.streaminer.stream.classifier.tree.RegressionTree
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Classifier<Data,Double>, Learner<Data,PredictionModel<Data,Double>>, Regressor<Data>, Model, PredictionModel<Data,Double>

    public class RegressionTree
extends AbstractRegressor<Data>

    This class implements a regression tree. A regression trees is a model tree, i.e. an induced decision tree with prediction models at its leafs. In case of the regression tree these prediction models are simply regression models.

    Author:
    Mattias Balke, Christian Bockermann <christian.bockermann@udo.edu>
